Diabetes Prediction ML System

A simple, production‑ready machine learning pipeline that predicts diabetes using medical data. It includes EDA, preprocessing, model training, evaluation, and a Flask API packaged with Docker.

Key Points

Dataset: 768 patient records

Best model: XGBoost (F1‑Score 0.71)

Handles class imbalance

Fully containerized API

How to Run
Clone the repo, install requirements, and start the API, or run it directly with Docker.

Features

Clean ML pipeline

Model comparison (LogReg, Random Forest, XGBoost)

StandardScaler preprocessing

REST API for predictions

Docker deployment

